<plot>From writer/Director Steve Rahaman, comes the story of two hired hit men who are forced to work on Christmas Day. Anthony (Richard Giambalvo), a family man who is tired of the life he leads, desperately tries to convince his friend and partner, Marcus (Daniel Girace) that his life needs to change. Caught between the woman he loves Danelle (Allyson Sereboff), and the intimidating mob boss, Don Silio (Michael Victor), who dictates his every move, Anthony must confront his present in order to save his future. Unfortunate events lead to disaster, when power overcomes friendship and loyalty reigns above all.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?104908</url></doc>
